(120, '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-431b4b8c-a8b9-3dbf-5f04-089e90020806"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">我们暂时只支持支付宝和智付充值。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-431b4b8c-a8b9-3dbf-5f04-089e90020806"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">此外，目前只支持人民币充值。不支持日元以及其他外币。</span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: blue; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">1. 支付宝充值</span></span></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-431b4b8c-a8b9-3dbf-5f04-089e90020806"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">成功注册会员后，即可使用支付宝进行充值。</span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.38; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">即时到账。</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: blue; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">2. 银联充值</span></span></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">暂不支持。</span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: blue; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">3. 其他方式充值</span></span></h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-431b4b8c-a8b9-3dbf-5f04-089e90020806"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-431b4b8c-a8b9-3dbf-5f04-089e90020806"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">暂不支持其他方式充值，请您见谅。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(114, '<div class="p1"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">您选择使用日本转运后，除您设置的账户ID和密码外，您还需了解并同意以下关于账户的使用说明：</span></span></div>\r\n<div class="p2">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="p1" style="color: blue;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#8b4513;"><strong><u><span class="s1">1．关于账户充值</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<div class="p1"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">目前仅支持支付宝即时到帐充值，银联充值后续开放。</span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="p1" style="color: blue;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#8b4513;"><strong><u><span class="s1">2．关于账户余额</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<div class="p1"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">账户管理中显示账户余额，其中账户余额如无特别说明， 您可以使用账户余额，按标准价格支付运单费用和其他费用。账户余额支持退款，退款需支付支付宝手续费，如参与充值返利活动的账户余额申请退款，返利金额将从中扣除。</span></span></div>\r\n<div class="p2">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class="p1" style="color: blue;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#8b4513;"><u><strong><span class="s1">3．关于删除会员账户</span></strong></u></span></span></p>\r\n<div class="p1"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">如果会员存在违反我们使用条款等行为，我们有权停止该用户的的使用。最终解释权归日本转运所有。</span></span></div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(115, '<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; line-height: 1.38; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Hello，小编在这里给您如何注册会员。真心很简单。</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">小编带您一步步的走，就更简单啦！请叫我雷锋啦~</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong>Step.1.</strong> 点击首页的【注册】链接。或者点击下面这个链接。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href="/index.php?m=member&amp;c=index&amp;a=register&amp;siteid=1"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);">免费注册会员</span></a></strong></p>\r\n<p><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718063302201.png" style="height: 365px; width: 900px;" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong>Step.2. </strong>在注册页面填写您的相关信息，并点击【注册按钮】。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">每一个输入框，我们都有为您做核查，如果输入内容有误，网站会提示您输入信息有误哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718063318174.png" style="width: 383px; height: 450px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong>Step.3.</strong> 注册完成后，会为您自动跳转到【我的后台】页面，也就是会员页面。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">需要您完善资料后才能使用转运服务。您会看到如下的提示框，请点击OK按钮。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718063333234.png" style="width: 298px; height: 200px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong>Step.4. </strong>我们会为你自动跳转到个人信息修改页面，请您在这个页面补全您的相关信息。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">带星号的均为必填项，请您务必填写。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718063350823.png" style="width: 602px; height: 995px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong>Step.5. </strong>系统会为您登录数据，并自动跳转到【我的仓库】页面。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718063410356.png" style="width: 1054px; height: 452px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">恭喜您，您已经是我们的会员啦！是不是很简单？</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2762cc5a-7c58-7414-7636-8ac2cfcbe1d1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">那么，快快开始您的购物旅程吧！</span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(158, '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38; background-color: transparent;">上传的证件人姓名必须和收件人名一致。</span><br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38; background-color: transparent;">收件地址可以根据实际情况，不需要和身份证一致。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(139, 69, 19);"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38; background-color: transparent;"><u><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;">修改方法</span></strong></u></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38; background-color: transparent;">注册会员后，进入【我的仓库】，</span><br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.38; background-color: transparent;">点击【用户信息】的子菜单【个人资料】进行修改。</span>', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(121, '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">写了这么多文章，终于到了小编我最喜欢的环节了。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">那就是&ldquo;骗钱&rdquo;的环节。呵呵。开个玩笑。有没有觉得小编萌萌哒？ ：P</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">言归正传，在这里给您介绍一下如何使用支付宝充值。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step1</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. 进入【我的仓库】页面，滑动页面到底部，点击页面右上方的【充值】按钮，或者点击左侧边栏的【在线充值】菜单。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081727987.png" style="width: 499px; height: 253px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">或者您点击这里。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081740346.png" style="width: 259px; height: 325px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step2</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. 点击【支付宝】菜单，进入支付宝充值页面。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081755580.png" style="width: 732px; height: 383px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step3</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. 输入您的充值金额，并点击【下一步】按钮。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">小编比较穷，就只充值1元啦。您可要多充值些哦。不然余额不足还要再充值呢。麻烦死啦~</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081808426.png" style="width: 644px; height: 486px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step4</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. 输入您的充值金额，并点击【确认充值】按钮。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081822545.png" style="width: 700px; height: 406px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">. &nbsp;系统会自动引导您进入支付宝付款页面。在这个页面您可以根据喜好选择您的付款确认方式。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">您可以选择手机扫描二维码付款，也可以选择电脑版付款。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在这里小编为您提供二种方式详细步骤供您参考。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">使用手机扫描二维码付款:</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.1.</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> &nbsp;打开您的手机支付宝客户端，点击页面左上方的【扫一扫】。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081839802.png" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.2.</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> 扫描电脑页面显示的二维码。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081859668.png" style="width: 708px; height: 472px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.3. </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">确认付款金额后，点击【确定】按钮进入下一步。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081921600.png" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.4. </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">点击提示弹框的【确定】按钮付款。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718081958165.png" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.5. </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">系统会自动为您完成付款流程，经过几次自动的系统跳转后，系统会为您自动跳 &nbsp;转回【我的仓库】页面。在这里您可以查看流水账单查看您的充值记录。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082017734.png" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">使用电脑版支付宝付款:</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.6.</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> &nbsp;点击页面右下方的【登录账户付款】。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082038630.png" style="width: 956px; height: 464px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.7.</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> &nbsp;点击页面右下方的【登录账户付款】。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082051359.png" style="width: 963px; height: 457px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.8.</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> &nbsp;确认付款金额后，输入您的支付宝支付密码病点击【确认付款】按钮进入下一步。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-left: 36pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082103927.png" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Step5.9. </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">系统会自动为您完成付款流程，经过几次自动的系统跳转后，系统会为您自动跳 &nbsp;转回【我的仓库】页面。在这里您可以查看流水账单查看您的充值记录。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082116860.png" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">恭喜您， 您已经成功完成了充值！！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-451d8e3f-80c1-b0e4-1eb1-83fecc339523"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">祝您有个愉快的转运体验！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(122, '<h1 class="p1"><span style="font-size:14px;"><kbd>如果您需要退款，请发邮件至客服，并在邮件内注明您的支付宝或银行账户信息及申请退款金额。</kbd></span></h1>\r\n<br />\r\n<p class="p1"><span style="font-size:14px;"><kbd>为了保护您以及我们的共同利益，请您遵守以下规定：</kbd></span></p>\r\n<div class="p2"><kbd><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">1</span></span><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;">.</span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">&nbsp;&nbsp;当您的所有运单全部处理并结算完毕后，我们才能开始您的账户余额退款手续。</span></span></kbd><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="p2"><kbd><span style="font-size: 14px;">2</span><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;">.</span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span class="s1">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 14px;">我们在审核确认您的运单处理完结后，在2-3个工作日内退款到您指定的支付宝或银行账户。</span></kbd></div>\r\n<div class="p2"><br />\r\n<kbd><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span class="s1">3</span></span><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;">.</span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span class="s1">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">为了确保您的账户安全，退款的账户人名必须与收款账户(支付宝、银行卡)人名一致，否则，我们将不予处理。</span></span></kbd></div>\r\n<div class="p2"><br />\r\n<kbd><span style="font-size: 14px;">4</span><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px;">.</span><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span class="s1">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span class="s1">如果您充值时，参与了充值返利等活动，退款时，我们将从退款中扣除返利金额。</span></span></kbd></div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(123, '<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.38;">今天，小编给您介绍一下如果进行运单查询。</span></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我们在首页为你准备了一个运单查询框。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">使用方式很简单，</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">如果您是</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">日本邮政的邮单</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">，不论您是日本国内的运单还是国籍运单，都可以在首页的运单查询框进行查询。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082600628.png" style="width: 313px; height: 271px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">如果您是其他快递公司的邮单，请点击快递查询框下方的链接。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082611339.png" style="width: 319px; height: 264px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">系统会为您自动跳转到运单查询页面。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在运单查询页面，我们为您提供了各种运单查询的链接。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">您可以点击对应的链接进行运单查询。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718082621828.png" style="width: 805px; height: 295px;" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我们还在努力和其他快递公司做对接，将来争取可以实现所有快递公司的快件一键查询。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5ed93ad3-828b-6409-567f-f75b3442e562"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">还请您再等待一下哦。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
(173, '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.38;">日淘嘛，您肯定最关心的就是费用啦。</span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">为了方便您查询，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我们为您提供了两种费用查询的方式。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在这里，让小编为您简单介绍一下。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">小编最喜欢这种助人为乐的事情啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">第一种，使用主页的费用查询框的方式。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这个，真心很简单。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在首页右下方有一个浮动的边框，点击上方的费用查询按钮。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718071402737.png" style="width: 854px; height: 406px;" /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">系统会为您弹出一个费用查询的弹框。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在框内输入货物的重量，即可计算出各种邮递方式的大致费用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718071503662.png" style="width: 648px; height: 377px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">怎么样，方便吧？</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这第二种方式呢，更直白一些。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我们为您准备了一个费用的对照表。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">您可以点击以下链接来查看费用对照表。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">常见的转运方式货物重量以及运费对照表</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">注意哦，以上方式查找出来的费用仅供您参考。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">因为费用还需要包括包裹箱等的重量的哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">好了，费用查询已经给您介绍完啦，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">您可以开始日网购物啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-89c66dfb-8273-48ed-3b4a-d2844c9d0794"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">祝您有个愉快的购物体验~</span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0');
