(154, '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">こんにちは。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Hello， 既然您来到了这个页面，想必您是一个海淘或者日淘的新手呢。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">其实，小编有很多朋友都想日淘，但是，总觉得日淘好复杂。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在这个扫地都可以用机器人的年代，一切都是高大上的。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这个环境下，如果您没点日货，怎好和朋友愉快的聊天？<br />\r\n别再犹豫了！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">快快和小编一起读读下面的图表，来了解一下如何使用日本转运完成一次快捷又实惠的日淘购物吧。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718063836640.png" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">怎么样，是不是很简单？</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">是不是觉得手痒心动了呢？</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">那么快快点击下面的链接，学习一下如何使用吧。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">新手上路</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">在这里页面里，小编给您准备了使用方法，注册方法，购物方法。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-3bf8e164-7c79-252c-980a-df43d16a9d1b"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">希望您从此有个愉快的日淘体验！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
