rgin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d9e79f28-5d7a-f1f2-714e-c8210523590b"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718073319634.png" style="width: 589px; height: 523px;" /></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d9e79f28-5d7a-f1f2-714e-c8210523590b"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Step.5: 注册后自动跳转到Amazon的主页。请查看一下当前用户的注册名称，如果是您的姓名，则注册成功。确认方法很简单，就是看一下当前登录的用户名。</span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d9e79f28-5d7a-f1f2-714e-c8210523590b"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718073334224.png" style="width: 1100px; height: 116px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-d9e79f28-5d7a-f1f2-714e-c8210523590b"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">好嘞，恭喜您，您现在已经拥有了日本Amazon官网的账号喽！可以畅享Amazon的贴心服务喽！</span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0');
INSERT INTO `t_news_data` (`id`, `content`, `readpoint`, `groupids_view`, `paginationtype`, `maxcharperpage`, `template`, `paytype`, `relation`, `voteid`, `allow_comment`, `copyfrom`) VALUES
(157, '<span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">今天，小编给您介绍如何在日本乐天市场购物。本篇文章面向</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">初次购物者</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">。如果您已经是常客了，您可以选择跳过本文章的部分内容，也可以参考小编的另一边文章---- </span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><strong>手把手教您乐天购物（非初次购物者篇）</strong>。</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">希望小编的这些文章可以助您购物一臂之力。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">此外，在您进行购物前，您需要拥有一个日本乐天的账号。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">如果你还没有账号，请参考以下文章来申请一个账号。</span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><strong><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><a href="http://ex1.sunyl.com/index.php?m=content&amp;c=index&amp;a=show&amp;catid=19&amp;id=151" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">手把手教您注册日本乐天账号</span></span></a></span></strong></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">OK了。说了这么多废话，终于可以进入正题了。其实购物也蛮简单的，让小编慢慢给您道来。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Step.1</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">: 挑选好您喜欢的商品。如果您已经知道链接，那么点击该链接，直接进入店铺网页。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">如果您还没有链接，那么请使用搜索功能来搜索您想要的商品。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">您可以使用商品代码，商品名称，品牌等关键字来进行搜索。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">如果您不知道您想要的商品的日文名称，那么推荐您使用</span><strong><a href="http://fanyi.baidu.com/#zh/jp/" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">百度翻译</span></span></a></strong><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">或者</span><strong><a href="http://translate.google.cn/" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">google翻译</span></span></a></strong><span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">小编现在也没什么想要的，就用葡萄酒来给您做示范啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">在首页的搜索栏输入您的关键字。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718074600922.png" /></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#ee82ee;"><strong><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Step.2: </span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">在检索结果中挑选您中意的商品，点击商品名称的链接进入商品的详细页面。</span></span></strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718074615862.png" /></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#40e0d0;"><strong><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Step.3:</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> 点击详细页面的【買い物かごに入れる】按钮将商品加入购物车。这是一个十分浩大的工程。日本乐天的页面很难找到这个按钮。您要细心的滑动页面直到您找到它。</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#40e0d0;"><strong><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">点击后，会自动跳转到购物车页面。</span></span></strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718074641231.png" style="width: 407px; height: 325px;" /></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#ffa07a;"><strong><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">在某些商家这个按钮也有可能长成这个样子。只要是带了【買い物かごに入れる】字样的按钮，就对啦。</span></span></strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718074655440.png" style="width: 253px; height: 71px;" /></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#ee82ee;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Step.4:</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> &nbsp;在购物车页面确认您的商品数量，如果无误您就可以选择【ご購入手続き】按钮进行结算。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#ee82ee;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">如果您还想追加其他商品，您可以选择【元の商品に戻り、買い物を続ける】按钮回到商品页面继续购物。</span></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718074709886.png" /></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="color:#40e0d0;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4ece"><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Step.5:</span><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> 根据您当前的登录状况，在这里有可能会需要您再次输入用户名和密码。请不要惊慌，输入用户名和密码就可以成功跳转到付款页面了。</span></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-04145284-5d7b-e435-9681-2525463d4e