(183, '最近大热的酵素减肥法其实在日本已经风行多年了。酵素减肥，即是利用属于食品的酵素产品，边调整身体的机能，边消耗过剩的脂肪，让身体变得更健康，脖子、背部、腹部、大腿等处的脂肪也都消失了，而使整个人变得轻松自在。台湾女星林依晨便是使用酵素断食法成功减肥4公斤。下面就为大家介绍几款日本最疯卖的瘦身酵素。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)"><strong>生酵素 222种天然水果植物浓缩精华提取物 酵素 60粒</strong></span>　<br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713122456143.png" style="width: 750px" /><br />\r\n　　日本乐天No1生酵素222种天然植物水果浓缩精华,它是天然的酵素。仅通过每日饮食难以摄入的量,222种以上的自然材料,原封不动封入胶囊之中，方便您服用,均衡每日营养,获取因食材的加热处理而无法获取的营养元素,比生吃蔬菜更轻松便捷。给希望实现健康身体的人士的补充剂。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">食用方法</span>：</strong>1日2粒，无需咀嚼，用水或温水送服。（最好饭前吃）<br />\r\n<address>\r\n	<kbd><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_noss_1?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=生酵素+222&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3A生酵素+222" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">购买地址</span></a></kbd></address>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)"><strong>日本metabolic 酵素&times;酵母 活性发酵瘦身消脂</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713122522646.jpg" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n这款由天然植物提取出的酵素促进人体新陈代谢，补充蔬菜水果的营养摄入不足，提高免疫力，帮助肝脏排毒，它也是美容瘦身乐天销量第一的酵素。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">食用方法</span>：</strong>一天1次，一次2粒，温水内服，饭前30分钟左右空腹吃，建议中或晚餐前吃。<br />\r\n<address>\r\n	<kbd><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_ss_i_1_9?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=metabolic酵素x酵母&amp;sprefix=metabolic%2Caps%2C443&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3Ametabolic酵素x酵母" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">购买地址</span></a></kbd></address>\r\n<br />\r\n<p><kbd><strong style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 26px"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">日本<span lang="EN-US">ISDG</span>医食同源 爽快酵素粒 神奇植物弗斯可林&times;双歧乳酸菌</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713123100814.jpg" style="height: 944px; width: 600px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">　这款酵素由</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">121</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">种果蔬发酵，加入神奇植物弗斯可林提取物，减肥效果明显，同时添加儿童用级别的双歧杆菌</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">,</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">有效改善肠内环境。除了有减肥功效之外</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">,</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">长期服用可以有效改善体质，是一款男女老少皆宜的产品！它由日本女星熊田曜子代言，是在日本每</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">40</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 19.5pt">秒钟卖出一袋的超人气单品！</span></kbd></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><kbd><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">食用方法：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">一天<span lang="EN-US">2</span>次，一次<span lang="EN-US">1-2</span>粒，温水内服，建议早晨空腹和晚上睡前服用。</span></kbd><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_noss_1?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=医食同源ドットコム+爽快酵素&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3A医食同源ドットコム+爽快酵素" style="line-height: 19.5pt" target="_blank">购买地址</a></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><br />\r\n<kbd><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">日本资生堂八分饱习惯丸酵素</span></strong><br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713124721601.jpg" /><br />\r\n<span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">现在的人就是吃不控制，每次都吃到撑，但就是改变不了习惯，这样对身体也不好，这个可以让你养成八分饱的习惯。它刚推出就在<span lang="EN-US">cosme</span>上好评不断，据官方统计资料，一个月不运动不刻意节食也可以</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">减重</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">3kg</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">，主要成分酵素、乳酸菌，一天两粒固定时间服用。</span><br />\r\n<strong style="line-height: 19.5pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">食用方法：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">一天<span lang="EN-US">2</span>粒（建议饭前半小时服用）用温水吞服</span></kbd></p>\r\n<address style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt">\r\n	<a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_ss_c_0_4?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=资生堂八分饱&amp;sprefix=资生堂八%2Caps%2C350&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3A资生堂八分饱" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">购买地址</span></a></address>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><br />\r\n<kbd><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">日本<span lang="EN-US">Natural Healthy Standard</span>青汁酵素瘦身代餐粉</span></strong><br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713122619574.jpg" style="height: 502px; width: 750px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 20.25pt">Natural Healthy Standard&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 20.25pt">青汁酵素瘦身水果代餐粉是一种方便于日常食品或饮用的营养均衡产品。由<span lang="EN-US">200</span>多种蔬菜和水果制成的，每天喝一杯代餐减肥的同时还能补充维生素，不流失营养，还能排毒美容的调理身体各种亚健康，是非常好的选择！有多款口味可以选择：蜂蜜味<span lang="EN-US">/</span>芒果味<span lang="EN-US">/</span>樱桃味等。正常人一顿饭是摄入<span lang="EN-US">600</span>&mdash;<span lang="EN-US">800</span>大卡的热量，这款代餐粉<span lang="EN-US">2</span>勺<span lang="EN-US">=23</span>大卡，就能代替一餐。没有副作用，还可以加快新陈代谢，调整内分泌。</span></kbd></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><kbd><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">食用方法：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">晚餐<span lang="EN-US">2</span>勺，推荐代晚餐食用，效果最好。</span></kbd></p>\r\n<address style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt">\r\n	<a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_noss_2?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=Natural+Healthy+Standard　　" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">购买地址</span></a></address>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><br />\r\n<kbd><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">日本<span lang="EN-US">ORIHIRO NIGHT DIET</span>果蔬睡眠瘦身 新谷酵素<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0705/20150705043338388.jpg" style="height: 500px; width: 500px" /></span></strong><br />\r\n<span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">新谷酵素</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">ORIHIRO NIGHT DIET</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">夜迟酵素</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">30</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">包 加强版！分解力大大提升！抑制糖分吸收，燃烧过剩能量，鲜活酵素冻干技术，一包酵素分解米饭</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">10.4</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">碗，砂糖</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">204g</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">，蛋糕</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">6.46</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">块，啤酒</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">68.7</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">杯！针对熬夜，夜宵，饮食不规律，甜食爱好者，吃过之后排泄通畅，不拉肚子也不会腹痛！</span><br />\r\n<strong style="line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">食用方法：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 21pt">睡前半小时服用，一天一包。</span></kbd></p>\r\n<address style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt">\r\n	<a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_noss_2?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=夜遅いごはんでもDIET&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3A夜遅いごはんでもDIET" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">购买地址</span></a></address>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><br />\r\n<kbd><strong style="font-size: 16px"><span lang="JA" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">日本お嬢様公主酵素原液</span></strong><br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713123523719.jpg" /><br />\r\n<span lang="JA" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">お嬢様公主果蔬酵素原液，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">720ml</span><span lang="JA" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">纯天然酵素，日本公主酵素是市面上口感最好，唯一可以带来饱食感的活性酶，改变酸性体质，作用：减脂，改善肤质，提高活力与睡眠质量，调理肠胃，排毒，驻颜。</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">由<span lang="EN-US">64</span>野生有机天然原料<span lang="EN-US">+22</span>种新鲜蔬菜经过长达<span lang="EN-US">700</span>多天（<span lang="EN-US">2</span>年）！　　</span><br />\r\n<strong style="line-height: 19.5pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">食用方法：</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">每天一次，每次倒<span lang="EN-US">30</span>毫升酵素冲上<span lang="EN-US">150</span>毫升温水、苏打水或者蔬菜汁稀释都是可以的，代替晚餐，喝酵素前后<span lang="EN-US">2</span>个小时不能吃任何东西。</span></kbd></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><kbd><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">【<span lang="EN-US">48</span>小时法】：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">每次<span lang="EN-US">60ml</span>公主酵素加<span lang="EN-US">300</span>毫升的水、果汁等稀释。两日内每隔<span lang="EN-US">3</span>小时左右饮用一次，代替一切进食。夜里不需要喝，两天基本喝完一瓶公主酵素！</span></kbd><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt"><kbd><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60)">【<span lang="EN-US">24</span>天法】：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">每次<span lang="EN-US">30ml</span>公主酵素加<span lang="EN-US">150</span>毫升的水、果汁等稀释，每天代替一餐饮用，代餐晚餐的话瘦身效果最好。一瓶能喝大约<span lang="EN-US">24</span>天！</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(222,58,60); line-height: 19.5pt">【 建 议 】：</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 19.5pt">以上两种方法可以结合使用也可以轮番使用！三瓶为一个疗程！推荐<span lang="EN-US">24</span>天法，减掉多，还健康！水温要低于<span lang="EN-US">30</span>摄氏度！冷水或温冷水最佳！</span></kbd></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 20.25pt"><kbd><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">建议大家用<span lang="EN-US">24</span>天法，这样身体的吸收会比较好，体现出来的效果也会更好，<span lang="EN-US">48</span>小时法，会因为个体吸收的快慢，效果体现的也不一样，有的<span lang="EN-US">MM</span>或许<span lang="EN-US">3-5</span>天才会明显感觉到，心急的<span lang="EN-US">MM</span>就会觉的效果差强人意。</span></kbd></p>\r\n<address style="font-size: medium; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0,0,0); margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 20.25pt">\r\n	<a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=nb_sb_ss_c_0_4?__mk_ja_JP=カタカナ&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps&amp;field-keywords=お嬢様公主酵素&amp;sprefix=お嬢様公主酵素%2Caps%2C365&amp;rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3Aお嬢様公主酵素" style="line-height: 19.5pt; text-indent: 20.25pt" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(255,0,0)">购买地址</span></a></address>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0');
