(171, '<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 1.38; background-color: transparent">嘿，小编今天心情十分不错，准备放个大招，教您如何注册日本Amazon的Prime会员。</span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">但是，进入正题之前，先让小编给新手们扫个盲。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">什么是Amazon的Prime会员？</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.9636"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">日本的Amazon和国内的Amazon不同，</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">是不提供任意金额免运费服务的。貌似国内现在已经改为满29元免邮。小编对国内行情不太熟悉，如果信息有误，还请您给小编留个言，小编好修改修改。Prime会员就是日本Amazon提供的解决这个问题的方法。当然也是Amazon赚钱的方法之一。呵呵。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">Amazon的Prime会员有什么好处？</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">Amazon的Prime会员好处总结一下，只有三点。但是每一点都很犀利。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">第一点，发货速度。 </span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">最短当天就可以收到货物。这是大Amazon的主推牌。小编很是喜欢Amazon，经常买货，一般都是隔天就到。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">第二点，每个月可以免费阅读一本kindle的电子书。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">这个也是犀利的很。如果您有kindle，那么就可以每个月都下载一本免费的电子书。不过，是不能同时拥有两本以上的免费电子书的。必须要看完一本您再下载另一本。不过，免费的，还求什么呢。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">第三点，不定期的会员增值服务。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">Amazon会有不定期的会员增值服务，比如买Kindle返3000日元的返券。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">不过也不是每天都有的。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">Amazon的Prime会员贵么？</span></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent">Amazon的Prime会员标准价位是 3900日元(含税)/年。如果您经常购物，这个是绝对划算的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">所以小编在这里给您介绍个免费注册Prime的方法。这个免费Prime会员只能免费使用一个月，一个月后会自动收费的。不过不用担心，小编会在这里教你怎么注册和怎么取消滴。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">好了，不说废话啦， 给您来点实料吧。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51,51,51)">Step.1: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">打开Amazon的逛网，登录到Amazon。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">Amazon官网链接：</span><strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp" style="text-decoration: none"><span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">www.amazon.co.jp</span></span></a></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51,51,51)">Step.2: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">点击顶部菜单的【今すぐ登録プライム】按钮。</span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718080558307.png" style="height: 90px; width: 750px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51,51,51)">Step.3: </span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">点击页面右方的【30日間の無料体験を試す】按钮。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718080747123.png" style="height: 264px; width: 750px;" /></span></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51,51,51)">Step.4:</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">系统会自动为您跳转到登录页面，不用惊慌，正常登录即可。根据您的登录状态，这个页面也有可能不出现的。如果没有出现这个页面，请直接进入下一步的操作。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(51,51,51)">Step.5:</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)"> 在登录页面输入您的信用卡和地址信息，点击提交按钮。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">请根据小编的提示正确填写您的信用卡信息和地址。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">此外，小编还为您列出了输入时的注意事项，请您仔细阅读后再输入哦！</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">信用卡:请正确填写您的信用卡信息，本次注册不会收取您任何费用，只是需要输入卡号等信息。如果信用卡信息不正确，会报错的哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 1.38"><span id="docs-internal-guid-509041db-8129-5c09-4e36-8e2598476a39"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(51,51,51)">地址:如果您没有日本境内地址，您可以选择使用转运的地址。为了方便您输入，小编给您列在这里，您复制粘贴就行啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 0pt">\r\n<table style="border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; border-collapse: collapse; border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none">\r\n<colgroup>\r\n	<col width="126" />\r\n	<col width="498" />\r\n</colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n	<tr style="height: 0px">\r\n	<td style="border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0,0,0); vertical-align: top; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 7px; border-bottom-color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-top: 7px; border-right-style: solid; padding-left: 7px; border-left-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-right: 7px">\r\n	<p dir="ltr" style="m