(174, '<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713114721928.jpg" style="height: 598px; width: 750px;" /><br />\r\nhttp://px.a8.net/svt/ejp?a8mat=2C0PLX+84BUSY+249K+BWGDT&amp;a8ejpredirect=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fdp%2FB008UNXVIW%2F%3Ftag%3Da8-affi-216356-22<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:18px;">一、生酵素的八大好处：</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n1、调节机能：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:14px;"> 促进新陈代谢，营养消化、吸收、合成、酵素营养充足。身体机能与精神状态才会好。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:18px;"><strong><span style="font-size:16px;">2、助抗氧化</span></strong>：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:14px;">丰富抗氧化物S0D，延缓衰老。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">3、美容养颜：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:14px;">清理体内腐败菌，减少有毒物质对皮肤的损害，起到良好的美容作用。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>4、排毒瘦身：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;"> &nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;">可清理肠胃道、增强排毒，改善新陈代谢，从里到外起到瘦身作用。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">5、净化血液</span></strong>：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">分解血液中过多的胆固醇和脂肪，化解污物，净化血管并促进循环。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">6、细胞赋活：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:14px;">促进细胞新生，帮助修复细胞。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">7、护肝解酒</span></strong>：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;"> &nbsp;补充酵素，使酒精分解加速。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">8、酸碱平衡：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size:14px;">改善酸性体质为弱碱性。PH值在735以下为酸性体质，会感到疲乏、亚健康等。恢复到弱碱性（PH7.35~7.45），人体体抗力能提高。</span><img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713114648165.jpg" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><strong>二、酵素的食用方法：</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、每次两粒，温水冲服，早晨或晚上服用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:18px;"><strong>三、注意事项：<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong> 服用酵素期间注意事项：请多饮水，食用果蔬，充足睡眠，适量运动会加快身体排出毒素；凉饮、温饮（温度不能超过50）均可；服用酵素期间，如果身体产生明显不适，可减量减饮服用，或饭后一小时服用，也可以暂停服用，待不适应消失后，再坚持服用，千万不要放弃，服用效果明显，短则数日，长则1-3月。</span></span><img src="/uploadfile/2015/0713/20150713114704442.jpg" /><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0'),
