3779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Dodonpa为您提供了一张300日元的优惠券。前提是，3000日元以上的商品才可以使用</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0pt 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">第二种，在活动对象的店家购买商品，最大有机会获得30倍的返点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0pt 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">乐天之所以有这么多用户，就是因为它有一个庞大的返点系统。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0pt 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">正常情况下的返点为1%，在dodonpa对象商店购买商品，在几家店内购买了，就可以获得几倍的返点。比如你在3家店分别购买了1000日元以上的商品，那么就可以获得3倍的返点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0pt 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">以此类推。。。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0pt 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">第三种，对象商品最大20倍返点。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0pt 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.38;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这个也是个经典的乐天返点促销，比第二种简单明了得多了。您可以去店里搜索返点倍数高的商品就可以了。</span></span></p>\r\n<br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; text-align: justify;" />\r\n<br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.03779527544975281px; text-align: justify;" />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', 0, 1, '|0');
