(29, '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.38;">Kindle一直想要一台。</span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">国内amazon上的官方售价是 499， 968.</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">听着数字有种笔记本电脑带回家的错觉。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">但是我之前一个朋友在日本买的kindle，据说是8000多日元，貌似没差很多。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">kindle paper的话，是要14280日元。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">听人说，日本的货总是要比国内的货好。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">一样子的价格，总觉得买国内阿码的货，有点亏了。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这不，正好看到了小编介绍的4000日元活动。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这节省了4000日元，邮费都有了。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">感觉赚赚哒。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">amaozn注册会员后，申请Prime 会员，然后订购一台kindle。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">kindle出了白色的，黑色的感觉大家都有了，于是我就弄了台白色的。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">因为是Prime会员，所以隔天到件，付款什么的搞定后，转运公司三天EMS到货。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">速度也是刚刚的。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">好了，既然是晒单还是上照片吧。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">为了纪念这漂洋过海的kindle，我特意做了一套隆重的开箱仪式。</span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718062133370.jpg" style="width: 800px; height: 1067px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718062157942.jpg" style="height: 600px; width: 800px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718062221358.jpg" style="width: 800px; height: 1067px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">接下来，是一套隆重的开机仪式。</span></span></p>\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718062241704.jpg" style="width: 800px; height: 1067px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718062259389.jpg" style="width: 800px; height: 1067px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718062316350.jpg" style="width: 800px; height: 1067px;" /><br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">OK了，感谢转运公司的光速转运。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-93b684a2-a064-f9c1-5d43-43754813ee92"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我要去继续体验我的全新的kindle去了。</span></span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1),
(31, '海淘真的很简单呢， 之前朋友淘了不少的宝贝，被我发现后，自己禁不住也想体验一下，这不就碰上日本亚马逊促销时抢了这么多的宝贝，而正在为转运发愁时，恰巧看到日本转运做返现活动，果断用了，我用的是EMS速度是相当的快了， 3天就收到货了。收到货心里好激动的说，哎呀，废话不多说，晒两张图吧，哈哈。 日本转运不要忘记返现哦。\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0806/20150806010648409.jpg" style="width: 440px; height: 587px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0806/20150806010706915.jpg" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0806/20150806030407891.jpg" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0806/20150806010731210.jpg" /></p>\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1),
(28, '<span style="font-size:14px;">又来晒单啦，这次定的东西不是着急用的让转运公司走的海运，没想到一箱产品一个月就到货了，</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">真的好快，超级</span>棒！！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0717/20150717090431202.jpg" style="width: 440px; height: 587px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0717/20150717090455194.jpg" style="width: 440px; height: 587px;" /><br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1),
(27, '晒单啦！！第一次日淘就这么成功，货到了以后迫不及待的拆开，感觉非常好，日本转运的EMS速度超快，10号拍下的14号就收到啦，推荐了几个朋友，下次还来。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0715/20150715022010218.jpg" style="width: 400px; height: 534px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0715/20150715022035987.jpg" style="width: 440px; height: 330px;" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src="/uploadfile/2015/0715/20150715085940175.jpg" /><br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1),
(30, '<div>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我还真不是一个喜欢晒单的人，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">但是转运公司既然返还邮费，就没有不晒的道理。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">谁会和钱过不去呢。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">你说，是不是。。。。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">虽说花王的蒸汽眼罩已经被写得烂了，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">既然我已经买了，还是决定要介绍一下下。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">转运时效</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我用的是ems，那速度当然就不用提了。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">天下的阿妈上prime购了，加ems，五天到货。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">没话可说。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">关于花王</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">先给大家普及一下日本花王公司的信息。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">花王的英文名字是 Kao。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">花王是家集团公司，销售的东西那可不是一个两个。是各种各样。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">最有名气的就是各种生活用品。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">关于产品线，大家可以去花王的官网看看啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">日文官网点</span><a href="http://www.kao.com/jp/" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这里</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">汉语官网点</span><a href="http://www.kao.com/cn/" style="text-decoration:none;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这里</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">关于蒸汽眼罩</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">花王的蒸汽眼罩是2014年上市的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">上市以后就引起了很大的凡响，评价不是一般的高，现在各大药妆店均有销售。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">可想而知，这影响力，效果必然很好。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">哎呀，说什么都没用，直接上图吧。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">蒸汽眼罩有5种味道，亲们可以根据自己的需要，选择不同的味道。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我最喜欢薰衣草香型和玫瑰香型。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">薰衣草的香味让人心情舒畅，特别适合睡眠的时候用呢。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">说了这么多，说好的用后感呢？</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">别着急，在这里呢~</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">用后感</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">首先，买回来的眼罩是这个这样子的。</span></span><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718055854599.jpg" style="width: 225px; height: 300px;" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我喜欢薰衣草味道的，所以吧，给大家也介绍薰衣草味道的哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">另外，请忽略的桌子，我是个穷人，只有这么个桌子的啦。哈哈。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">再来个反面的图片，都是日语的，看懂的朋友看看，看不懂的朋友就忽略了吧。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">然后呢，最关键的来啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">打开盒子，里面是5片独立的包装，每一片都是这个感觉的。</span></span><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718060040839.jpg" style="width: 225px; height: 300px;" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718060140483.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">别怕，我的是5片装的，所以里面是五片的，如果亲买的是14片的话，肯定是十四片哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">（以前有个mm问过一次类似的问题，我笑的胃疼，哈哈）</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">然后，我们再来拆开一层它神秘的面纱吧。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">于是就变成这样子了。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718060206617.jpg" style="width: 225px; height: 300px;" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">打开以后就是这样啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718060235999.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 225px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">来，给爷翻个身。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><img alt="" src="/uploadfile/2015/0718/20150718060300819.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 225px;" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">然后亲就可以把它带到眼睛上啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我的真实感受</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">好了，我们已经把眼罩小妞遍览了一番了，可以来体验一下眼罩小妞啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">眼罩打开包装后，大概10秒钟就开始发热。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">所以，千万不要打开了忘记带哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">那就浪费了呢。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">眼罩的温度，根据官方说法，大概是40度左右。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我的皮肤没有自带温度计，所以不是很清楚是不是真的有40度。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">但是，确实要比我们的正常体温高一些，带到眼睛上热乎乎的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这个温度大概能持续10-20分钟左右。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">夏天的话貌似持续的时间更长些，最近因为是冬天，感觉10多分钟就没有什么温度啦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">不过，即使是时间略短了，还是很有效果的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">眼睛周围会出一层薄薄的汗水。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">眼睛会觉得很轻松。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我的工作经常用电脑，每天下班回家了，眼睛又干又痛。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">用一用这个眼罩，真心轻松很多。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">另外，我偶尔会带隐形眼镜。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">一天下来也很辛苦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">用用这个眼罩，真心很舒服。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这款眼罩最舒心的就是，眼罩的带子是棉的，挂到耳朵特别舒服。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">晚上睡觉前带着也是OK滴。。。一点没有不舒服感哦。。。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这眼罩可以去黑眼圈，眼袋？</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我是个说实话的人，根据我的经验，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">黑眼圈，眼袋都不是一天形成的。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我经常失眠，所以黑眼圈，眼袋都有。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我对自己长相没信心，所以就不上照片了。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">用了这个眼罩以后呢，其实真的没什么效果。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">哈哈。你是不是以为我要说有效果？</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">真的没什么大得效果。可以适当的缓解，但是不治本。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">如果你是因为前一天喝水喝多了，眼镜水肿，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">用这个眼罩可以解决很多问题。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">长期失眠引起的眼袋和黑眼圈，请亲不要报太大的希望哦。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这眼罩多少米？</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">这眼罩吧，说便宜也不便宜，说贵吧，其实也不贵。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">我觉得，针对效果，对得起这个价钱。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">哎，拿人家的手短。。。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">转运公司的大侠们，看我写的这么辛苦的份上，</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">千万别忘记返还我的邮费呀。</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">不少米的说！</span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-e1b6e0f6-a08f-9c31-7d33-b423ad1b7bd1"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">小女子先谢过啦！</span></span></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', 0, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', '', 1),
